summary: The module contains test suites for the ONNX Stable Diffusion image-to-image pipeline, offering fast unit tests with synthetic inputs and comprehensive integration tests that run inference on GPU using a variety of sampling schedulers.
business_intent: Validate the correctness and performance of the ONNX Stable Diffusion Img2Img pipeline across different schedulers and hardware configurations to ensure reliable deployment and maintain high-quality image generation.
